snippet.textDisplay: I looked into making this a year ago and I think the reason it didn’t work is because 1: your corn flakes weren’t crushed enough and 2: your ice cream has to be sitting in your freezer for like a day or so to ensure that it gets hard enough that it won’t melt while handling (the fryer will warm it up to normal temp)
